- know where your money goes
- pay and buy everything you need at the beginning of the month
    to have a clearer idea of how much your monthly basic needs actually cost
    take advantage of bulk deals
    ensures your are covering ur basic needs first, before spending on xtra shit.
- familiarize urself with financial tools
- save with a purpose
    opportunity cost
    u will lose ur money in long run due to inflation
    saving money for retirement is a bad plan
    saving money for emergency situation or mortgage is a good plan
    
    
    
